productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Julisa has one of these. She works as a bartender and she says it looks crooked.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
I tried to nab it but got biscuit all over it.
one of my hobbies is poetry. and when i'm writing poems this works great.
My macaroni penguin loves to play with it.
